Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you human?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,M! How many are in pursuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}None.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems they gave up and resigned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we... b-beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Well done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They were on the run,\Nbut then she wiped them out in moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pink Devil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the corpse as a shield? That's harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She utilized the special rule\Nand took advantage of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Three teams left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Why? How? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your guidance up till now!\NThat mazelike route!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my unique player skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a kid,\NI've had a good sense of geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality or in games, I've never gotten lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I look at a map, I can draw it in my head,\Nno matter what kind of place it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name, "M," stands for "map"\Nor "mapper," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}That totally makes sense!\NIt's kind of cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,M! There are only three teams left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! We're guaranteed third place.\NA bronze medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pito told me we have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One team is in the desert wasteland.\NThey're over 5 km away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one is closer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we would need to detour around a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we'd reach them\Nwithin ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, sorry.\NLet's proceed along the waterfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least third place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if things work out,\Nwe may actually win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible, M?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They got hold of a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.80,Default,TEXT,0,0,0,,Death Game
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hovercrafts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll left to evade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,M, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do? Run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. They'd just come after us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How? We're on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hovercraft can go on flat land, too.\NThis place is perfect for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we run, they'll come after us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they've probably realized\Nit's just the two of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're good, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I run around as a decoy,\Nwhile you go hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good idea. But instead of running away,\NI'm going to shoot from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,M, are you desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it show?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What, an amazing weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,M, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a chicken,\Nso this is my too-chicken protective gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm their target, huh? That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}M, run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}M!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}You don't have to hit them! Just Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,M, that shield is incredible!\NTheir bullets can't get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bullets up to 7.62mm class will bounce off,\Neven at point-blank range.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't exist in reality, but in the game,\Nit's supposed to be space battleship armor plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's GGO's strongest material.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sold for an exorbitant price\Nat the underground materials store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they know how strong my shield is.\NThey'll likely all attack together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serpentine. Full speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the Bullet Lines appear,\Ndrop and roll to evade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll be shooting at them then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I wait for the Bullet Lines,\Nit'll be a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}True.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll talk later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take them out by the next scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, prepare to charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of Bullet Lines!\NWe'll go on land and attack from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake, you guys go right\Nand provide supporting fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,200 meters to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin containment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run around!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Come on! Try and tag me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}The Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}...I can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's two to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you get them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They took out Jake and Lax!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down! Dodge their Lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One hovercraft left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,M!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A deca-nade?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish him off, LLENN!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,M! I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were amazing!\NYou picked them off so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't they dodge the Bullet Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't see it? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it appears when you put your finger\Non the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't put my finger\Non the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the Bullet Circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it wouldn't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did you aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,LLENN, GGO is a game,\Nso a lot of things are simplified.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as shooting goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting is simplified?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For example,\Nif the real you had a real P90,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,could you shoot a target from 100 meters away\Nlike you can in GGO?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd probably be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality doesn't have system assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In GGO, if your target is in the Bullet Circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the game system will count that as a hit\Nwhen you fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The player thinks it's their own skill, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The assist increases your level
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and lets you obtain high performance guns,\Nwhich makes you stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made easy for the player,\Nso you can get better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like how I can run faster here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}In this way, center your target in the circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}then pull the trigger roughly,\Nso the gun moves slightly off-center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}So, what will happen to the bullet you fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll hit the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NRight in the middle of the Bullet Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The trigger of a GGO gun\Nis the same thing as a controller button.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Then what would happen in GGO if there was no assist\Nand you tried a difficult shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Firing an assault rifle from 100 meters away\Nwould consistently result in missed shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Without it, it'd be a laughable, crappy game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would play it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. A game's a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point\Nin making it completely realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how GGO should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pito, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone who was really good\Nat shooting in real life did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd wondered the same thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so I invited an acquaintance\Nwith real world shooting experience to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At first he was bewildered,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but soon got a feel for it\Nand hit the targets one after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is what he said after playing the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Bullet Circle is a double-edged sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thanks to the assist,\Nyou can hit your target without really aiming,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}so you're not getting\Nany real shooting practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, your skill will get rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So what's the upside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he said that this makes it extremely easy\Nto make long-distance shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In real life, it's really difficult to shoot\Nan enemy from far away. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that in the tutorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-distance shooting requires experience\Nand a lot of calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Real-life snipers,\Nwho don't have assist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,practice making hundreds of shots,\Nfiring and firing and firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they have thorough knowledge\Nof how bullets fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,M, you "aimed directly."\NYou didn't use the Bullet Circle assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You were firing without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked through the scope\Nand aimed using your own skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't put your finger on the trigger\Nuntil right before you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was no Bullet Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, M! That's a huge advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're winning! There's one team left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can beat them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get a gold medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I hope. It's almost time for the scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Oh. It's only been an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The scan's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they're still in the desert,\Nwe'll go to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, where are they? How far away are they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I've been shot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-A sniper?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weren't they... in the desert?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,LLENN, we're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Break out the medkit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I going to lose?\NAfter making it this far...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlikely they'll hit us at this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, they're moving across the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, have you seen any other enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't spotted any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's likely there are only two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head to the southwestern wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone, get on the truck!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's okay now.\NThey're over a kilometer away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, M, for getting shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're on guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not easy to spot a shooter\Nwho's 600 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more so if they're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll recover our hit points completely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a shot too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}They were so far away.\NHow did they get that close?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's the same as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}They got their hands on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a guess, but near the end of the game,\Nit's easier to find stuff all around
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that increases the teams' travel speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From vehicles with four-wheel-drive to trucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have a player who's a good driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get down about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lucky girl, LLENN.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't die from that sniper shot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the bullet had hit you 10 cm lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it would've damaged your heart or lungs,\Nkilling you instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy must've taken a questionable shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You lucked out there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were shot too, M.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They got lucky. And I'm a big target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the Line,\Nbut it was at my thigh, so I ignored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That sniper's rifle is 7.62 mm-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a narrow firing interval,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's equipped for automatic,\Nminimum ten-shot magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more annoying than a bolt-action.\NDon't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I swear I'll keep my guard up\Nuntil this is over. I won't be prideful either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promising answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we heading now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Southwest. We'll go ashore\Nin the wasteland you see on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better\Nto cross the lake and marshland?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much fuel left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee we could cross all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Things aren't exactly going our way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can defend here\Nand I can snipe from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy will be in the same situation,\Nbut we've got your agility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go west.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get further away and wait for the next scan\Nwith our backs to the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. This'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,M, before, were you about to read a letter?\NDid you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to read it at 15:00 exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more team. If we beat them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, with M's shield and shooting skills,\NI'm sure we'll win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,LLENN.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobody is going to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you move, I'll pull the trigger, M.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for telling me about the safety.\NIt came in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you try to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it this far,\Nall the way to the end, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To be killed and not know why\Ndoesn't sit right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't go on,\Nthen you should talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}If you're not gonna answer me, then fine!\NI'll fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, wait! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: Leave the Last Battle to Me.
